			            	-c "*‡∞∂‡±Å‡∞≠‡±ã‡∞¶‡∞Ø‡∞Ç* ‡∞à‡∞∞‡±ã‡∞ú‡±Å *‡∞™‡∞¶‡±ç‡∞Ø‡∞Ç*:" 

	#python3 telugu_padyalu.py	-m whatsapp \
